      "role": "user",
      "content": "but my doctor said it's super important to keep the levels consistent in my blood so i don't have any issues. if i skip it until tomorrow i might go way too high today. won't taking two now basically just make up for the one i missed so the level stays steady? it seems safer than just waiting.",
